summary: Credit cannot go unsaid. Markusliberty, thank you soo much. http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/5336052/?
descriptionHtml:
So, I noticed that Falkreath was suppose to be a good place for Imperials in Skyrim, considering it's owned by imperials and it's only a few feet from the border, so I wondered why there were so many nordic styled buildings there. So, I found a mod on the nexus for modders that adds the farmhouses for oblivion and got the best idea... I think you know what happened from here. It doesn't require that mod anymore, my bad. this used to be a copy-paste from my steam version.

------------------------------------------------ 

HUGE thanks to markusliberty for making the actual meshes and textures. http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/5336052/?

------------------------------------------------ 

Compatible with TAVE Falkreath, surprisingly. But that may just be my load order, so if you want 
to test it for me, that would be awesome. 

Goes well with another mod I made, Guard armors.[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=479359857]http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=479359857[/url]
